title: Enable Nested Virtualization in Nixos and Intel
tags: @zettel _method nixos intel
roam-id: 69eea7c2-0fb0-46e7-ba76-e5350ef1039c
type: text/markdown

``` nix
boot = {
  extraModprobeConfig = ''
      options kvm_intel nested=1
      options kvm_intel emulate_invalid_guest_state=0
      options kvm ignore_msrs=1
    '';
```
